1. *Ona* je *razmišljala* o njenoj budućnosti. (She was thinking about her future.)
2. On je *razmišljao* o tome šta će uraditi. (He was thinking about what to do.)
3. Ona je *razmišljala* da li da ode ili ostane. (She was thinking whether to go or stay.)
4. On se *razmišljao* o svojoj karijeri. (He was contemplating his career.)
5. *Razmišljala* je o svojoj porodici i njihovom zdravlju. (She was thinking about her family and their health.)